{"tid":1430292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要］掛住針對黑警黑社會，忘記左真正敵人","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T04:53:01.000Z","uid":140326,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"633755c34299bb831c04eedb47d843f301f98bd6","tid":1430292,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:57:37.000Z","msg":"呢段時間黑警同黑社會活躍起來，目的想激起民怨<br />\n<br />\n林鄭寫好曬劇本，要老屈示威者搞破壞<br />\n手足<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暫時轉陣，和平遊行</span></span>順便休息<br />\n等班狗同黑社會出到黎搵唔到目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n等到佢地以為民意減退，放低戒心果時<br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再出番黎勇武打狗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十號大埔點?<br />\n 手足門和平遊完就散，<br />\n留力訓下教補充體力，<br />\n拉長打持久戰，<br />\n等POPO繼續訓街<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">禍必及妻兒 要針對重點人物</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無恥林鄭月俄，<br />\n濫告 鄭若華，<br />\n濫捕 警務處(行動)副處長 鄧炳強，<br />\n鄉黑 何君堯</span>"},{"pid":"709320a87aeb858c28edd5e18637c96d9aa613d0","tid":1430292,"uid":268725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:58:17.000Z","msg":"Btw, 我會接機！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家集中火力推8月9-11日瘋狂接機呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n開始時間： 2019年8月9日下午1 點起<br />\n地點 ： 一號客運大樓機場接機大堂<br />\n1. 不申請不反對通知書<br />\n2. 和平靜坐，不衝擊不破壞不入禁區<br />\n3. Be water<br />\n4. 促政府答應五大訴求<br />\n5. 停止暴力打壓示威遊行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣有彩色、有黑白！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScTaC6X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScTaC6X.png&h=c0322113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJvwnn8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJvwnn8.png&h=c9585c21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ogUdAH8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FogUdAH8.png&h=872516f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96b92c869f406fc7013b5009a6c8a646d14ed987","tid":1430292,"uid":278243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:58:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13c5449e69a4599af2ba8c609852d268bdd7db4d","tid":1430292,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L17OqaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL17OqaU.jpg&h=8e4952ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcqHuCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcqHuCA.jpg&h=d468b84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJ8NFKg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZJ8NFKg.jpg&h=a40663df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pinuT4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpinuT4g.jpg&h=61ad88c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3100d2e6c685ea20bc934b2e077557c76fd2fa9f","tid":1430292,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"仲有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不合作運動升級</span></span><br />\n追擊TVB商場活動，杯葛廣告商"},{"pid":"e467d99b622c607bc65ddb29e6fd085088d2f5e0","tid":1430292,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:01:14.000Z","msg":"仲有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不合作運動升級</span></span><br />\n1823 不停投訴"},{"pid":"10887309bc4405910320104048954e4a1a2b083a","tid":1430292,"uid":140326,"like":0,"disl